Hi Trudy,

When editing the text box on a page using Elemetor, there is a bullet list icon that you can use in the text editor on the left side. That should automatically indent the bulleted list.

Here's a link of a short video: https://www.loom.com/share/cf310973df8b4013b7c67534bcbdfb5f

Hope that helps. Cheers!
